{"tid":186481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"US T錫克教男童獲准帶刀上學   香港對少數族裔支援應檢討","createTime":"2017-04-04T08:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T08:55:20.000Z","uid":82646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23dcaabb309e750479aae47fee29b39237f501c0","tid":186481,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:47:47.000Z","msg":"信奉錫克教 美國男童獲准帶刀上學<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1139353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1139353&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=3464bb7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1139353&h=31148d21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1139353</a><br />\n<br />\n2014-10-24  10:45<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSudMbbhYMfcd7wUncPRizMv_uUc8G3Kqs9kk3y3sjGUhvvDkTT2w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSudMbbhYMfcd7wUncPRizMv_uUc8G3Kqs9kk3y3sjGUhvvDkTT2w&h=fcba064f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國校園事件頻傳，因此許多地區嚴禁學生攜帶槍械武器上學，華盛頓州1名信奉錫克教（Sikh）的男童，被允許能以宗教信仰為由帶刀上學。<br />\n<br />\n錫克教徒在身上佩帶聖刀喀爾潘（Kirpan）以象徵勇氣，《今日美國》報導，華盛頓州奧本（Auburn）的吉爾多雷小學（Gildo Rey Elementary）有1名家裡信奉錫克教的男童，透過家長向學校協調，希望能佩帶聖刀上學。<br />\n<br />\n在學區主管查詢過州政府及聯邦政府的法條後，得知在某些情況下，華盛頓州的武器「零容忍」政策得允許特例存在，而且許多同樣信奉錫克教的教職員工及學生，同樣配帶聖刀多年且沒有發生任何問題。<br />\n<br />\n針對這次案例，學區副主管萊恩（Ryan Foster）表示學區允許男童可以佩帶聖刀，但必須藏在衣服內不得外露，學區的做法同時尊重信仰，也維護了其他學生的安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps 1985年印度航空182號班機遭受炸彈襲擊，機上乘客連機組人員共329人全部遇難。事後調查發現此次襲擊為錫克教恐怖分子策劃。"},{"pid":"4293f84abe468bd0b367707e019881d814e88d80","tid":186481,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"香港人又迫害南亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8510adc779f5e6ae8efbb06ecccc967b64546f","tid":186481,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個別例子 唔好針對佢地 我都識錫克教既人好nice好有教養<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你啦戇鳩"},{"pid":"f13a7fae608d8a8443886445ff1c6f14fb9eab55","tid":186481,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:53:25.000Z","msg":"咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c5b63b6841e1f70d0ad231a4efe3e3bb013a30","tid":186481,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人又迫害南亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明香港人點解比啲包容都唔得😕😠<br />\n有少少愛與和平 南亞人都唔會犯咁多事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}